{"tid":859951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【11狙擊手】選舉權竟非公民權利？？收皮啦","createTime":"2018-10-13T03:13:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T11:31:54.000Z","uid":138409,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"80a69d891fdbecb59175311f4d9c17ed9eec169a","tid":859951,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T03:13:11.000Z","msg":"又秒殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比卡超回歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n----------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=2325302090832783&amp;id=211789612184052&amp;comment_id=2325329000830092&amp;reply_comment_id=2325423970820595&amp;comment_tracking=%7B%22tn%22%3A%22R%2323%22%7D&amp;hc_location=ufi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2325302090832783%26id%3D211789612184052%26comment_id%3D2325329000830092%26reply_comment_id%3D2325423970820595%26comment_tracking%3D%257B%2522tn%2522%253A%2522R%252323%2522%257D%26hc_location%3Dufi&d=ebHhyDX2PSbaHo9MmOsjRP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=3e79b0f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=2325302090832783&amp;id=211789612184052&amp;comment_id=2325329000830092&amp;reply_comment_id=2325423970820595&amp;comment_tracking=%7B%22tn%22%3A%22R%2323%22%7D&amp;hc_location=ufi</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/EdInDisguise/posts/1912478005532141\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FEdInDisguise%2Fposts%2F1912478005532141&d=ebHhyDX2PSbaHo9MmOsjRP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=e76c33ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/EdInDisguise/posts/1912478005532141</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KDwHF6G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKDwHF6G.jpg&h=f7851663&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kXKNSdm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkXKNSdm.jpg&h=185f9d9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTong先生，閣下似乎不知&quot;國際人權公約&quot; 為何物。<br />\n<br />\n你多次聲稱被選權只是「公民權利」，而不是「人權」，「要有公民、憲制、國家框架才可有這（公民）權利。如果根本不承認這個國家，無理由認為自己有權利行使公民權利」：參見《明報》2018年1月29日的報導 （<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/....../s00001/1517192429728）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2F......%2Fs00001%2F1517192429728%EF%BC%89&d=ebHhyDX2PSbaHo9MmOsjRP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=644b0bcf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2F......%2Fs00001%2F1517192429728%EF%BC%89&h=b7359377\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/....../s00001/1517192429728）</a><br />\n<br />\n正如馮先生指出，此説完全並無本地人權法或國際人權法的法律根據。<br />\n<br />\n雖然《公民權利和政治權利國際公約》第25條字面上的意思似乎確是說，只有「公民」才有不受無理限制投票及被選的權利和機會。但這個語境下的「公民」，是指法律定義下的公民身分或者國籍，其中並不包括思想審查（例如必須認同當政者），才可以「公民」身分行使投票及被選的政治權利。<br />\n<br />\n在國際法層面上負責執行《公民權利和政治權利國際公約》的聯合國人權事務委員會在其1996年的《第25號一般性意見》第15和17段中清楚指出，「不得以無理或歧視要求如教育、居住或出身或政治派別等理由來排除本來有資格競選的人參加競選」；「不得以政治見解為由剝奪任何人參加競選的權利。」<br />\n<br />\n事實上，在以英女王為國家元首的英聯邦國家，例如加拿大甚至大不列顛及北愛爾蘭聯合王國本身，都不乏反對君主制的共和主義者參選。<span style=\"color: red;\">他們不會僅因為反對國家現行（甚至是最基本的）制度，而被拒絕視作「公民」</span>：如參見McGuinness v United Kingdom ECHR 1999-V 481第491頁；McAteer v Canada (Attorney General) (2014) 121 OR (3d) 1 (ONCA)。<br />\n<br />\n在這方面，歐洲人權法院已不止一次在其案例中指出，人民有權（在個人層面或透過行使結社自由）和平推動任何憲制改革，因他們須對國家與憲法付出的忠誠，<span style=\"color: red;\">只要求他們任何推動這些訴求的手段，沒有傷害民主本身，符合民主和和平的原則</span>：如參見The Socialist Party and Others v Turkey (1999) 27 EHRR 51 (GC); &Ouml;zdep v Turkey (2001) 31 EHRR 27 (GC); United Macedonian Organisation Ilinden-Pirin v Bulgaria (2006) 43 EHRR 52; Tanase v Moldova (2011) 53 EHRR 22 (GC); Republican Party of Russia v Russia (2015) 61 EHRR 20。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無論如何，其實《公約》第25條「每個公民」的字眼，經《香港人權法案》第21條的本地適應化後，在香港法律下已「翻譯」成「每個永久性居民」都有不受無理限制的投票和被選權。<br />\n<br />\n早於2000年年初的《陳華 訴 坑口鄉事委員會》一案中，時任上訴庭庭長黎守律（於《香港法律彙報與摘錄》第1卷第442G頁中）已經解釋，在香港的語境下，「永久居民」是《公約》第25條所指「公民」的同義詞。</span><br />\n<br />\n終審法院在同年的《律政司司長 訴 陳華》案（《香港終審法院彙報》第3卷第472A頁）亦明確指出，任何人只要屬永久居民，就有不受無理限制的投票及被選等政治權利，並無其他有關政治信念的額外要求。<br />\n<br />\n因此，選舉權（及被選舉權）當然屬人權，請弄清楚，不要混淆視聽，貽笑大方。"},{"pid":"7c080960e1b7bafa0c38bed87298de5a9b6f47e0","tid":859951,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T03:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8ae7245ef9bc82339d92432a371b281b1231c8","tid":859951,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T03:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ed23c9266cd3ca57341adc6cedd22d6a1b4b53","tid":859951,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T04:00:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"00f2f9c7167d015689f8c108afef57198ab16a82","tid":859951,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T04:05:01.000Z","msg":"不如去美國領使館請佢地派兵解放香港<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bGcbrS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bGcbrS</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},{"pid":"4b7ed58057c6a08a3a14b54f60736d065b160a78","tid":859951,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T13:44:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d46d95d72670d624954ae8e63e7e100a1b586e8c","tid":859951,"uid":56636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T13:47:39.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"21eb6cd05ac8ed29cf5a64f82b430844a3a80d51","tid":859951,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:20:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43666116b4f37727217cd4eec23120e96768b816","tid":859951,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:38:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a5d92ea23244f3c101c6a39ef4f0cd9db1f6633e","tid":859951,"uid":53481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T13:15:04.000Z","msg":"湯渣衰十一"},{"pid":"5a752030a9caa4f19506c1302ba6b7ff3744e750","tid":859951,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}